## CUSTOMIZING THE BOT

### Change the AI personality
Edit the `SYSTEM_PROMPT` in **`chatbot.py`** — this defines how the bot behaves.

### Use a different LLM
In `chatbot.py`, swap the LLM:
```python
# Anthropic Claude
from langchain_anthropic import ChatAnthropic
llm = ChatAnthropic(model="claude-3-5-haiku-20241022", api_key=os.getenv("ANTHROPIC_API_KEY"))

# Google Gemini
from langchain_google_genai import ChatGoogleGenerativeAI
llm = ChatGoogleGenerativeAI(model="gemini-1.5-flash", google_api_key=os.getenv("GOOGLE_API_KEY"))
```

### Add memory length control
Change `limit=10` in `main.py` to send more/fewer past messages as context.

