## TROUBLESHOOTING

| Problem | Solution |
|---|---|
| Webhook verification fails | Check `VERIFY_TOKEN` matches exactly in `.env` and Meta dashboard |
| Messages not received | Ensure you subscribed to `messages` webhook field in Meta |
| Supabase errors | Make sure you're using `service_role` key, not `anon` key |
| Cloud Run 500 errors | Check logs: `gcloud run logs read --service=whatsapp-chatbot` |
| Bot not replying | Check Cloud Run logs for LangChain/OpenAI errors |

